  "slug": "gilded-armor-lieonlion",
  "title": "LieOnLion's Gilded Armor",
  "description": "Adds Gilded Armor So Piglins won't attack",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/Gilded-Armor/img/gilder_armour_title(4k).png\" width=\"449\" height=\"200\" /></span></div>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/LieOnLion/main/Universal/strip.png\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/sA42pp6cuX\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=6800be&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\" /></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://github.com/LieOnLion/Enderite\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=6800be&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\" /></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@lieonlion\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=6800be&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\" /></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/lieonlion_/projects\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=6800be&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\" /></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/LieOnLion\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Patreon&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=6800be&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=patreon&amp;logoColor=white\" height=\"28\" /></a></div>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/LieOnLion/main/Universal/strip.png\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This mod adds Gilded Netherite And Enderite Armor.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Gilded Armor, once worn, will prevent Piglins from attacking just like gold armor.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Craft Gilded Armor by applying gold to Netherite or Enderite Armor in a Smithing Table.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Gilded Enderite Armor can also be crafted by applying an Enderite Ingot to a piece of Gilded Netherite Armor.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">!ENDERITE IS NOT NEEDED!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">So for those who don't want enderite, you will only be able to craft Gilded Netherite Armor.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Gilded Enderite will still show in creative menu.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Original idea was given to me by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Phweeeee\">Phweeeee</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;on GitHub</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This is a compatible version of <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/gildedarmor\">GildedArmor</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;* for my <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enderite-lieonlion\">LieOnLion's Enderite</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For Enderite, you can use most versions, but is recommended for Enderite 1.5 Anniversary Edition +</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">As textures match that version</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">* Check theirs out if u want<br />&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enderite-lieonlion\"><img src=\"https://lieonlion.github.io/Enderite/img/enderite-banner.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"40\" /></a>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/Gilded-Armor/img/gildedarmor-banner.png\" width=\"199\" height=\"40\" /></p>",
